data.name: ingresInsertCommand5.CommandText
data.value: INSERT into route ( rt_id, rt_airline, rt_flight_num, rt_depart_from, rt_arrive_to, rt_depart_at, rt_arrive_at, rt_arrive_offset, rt_flight_day ) VALUES ( next value FOR rt_id, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ? )

data.name: ingresSelectCommand5.CommandText
data.value: SELECT route.rt_airline, airline.al_iatacode, route.rt_flight_num, route.rt_depart_from, route.rt_arrive_to, route.rt_depart_at, route.rt_arrive_at, route.rt_arrive_offset, route.rt_flight_day, airline.al_name FROM route, airline WHERE route.rt_depart_from = ? AND route.rt_arrive_to = ? AND route.rt_flight_day LIKE ? AND route.rt_airline = airline.al_icaocode ORDER BY route.rt_airline, route.rt_flight_num

data.name: ingresUpdateCommand5.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE route SET rt_airline = ?, rt_flight_num = ?, rt_depart_from = ?, rt_arrive_to = ?, rt_depart_at = ?, rt_arrive_at = ?, rt_arrive_offset = ?, rt_flight_day = ? WHERE rt_airline = ? and rt_flight_num = ? and rt_flight_day = ?
